version_description: This version uses already established chords for the song and then tweaks them to fit a live version of the song. Whilst the other chords focus on the Studio version of the song, this set of chords focuses on a live version of chords and adds the picking pattern used in the live version of the song, something that has not been done by other tabs to date.
All the song's lyrics are written, along with the tab that goes in between the verses. All chords relative to Capo 2. Relatively easy to play.
Seafret - Beauty on the Breeze - Capo 2 - Link https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GotZdiR7stc.
